          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the shallot and garlic are softening, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 700ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1.05L] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Once softened, add your <strong>arborio rice</strong> and <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min or until the Chinese rice wine has evaporated</p>",
