      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked through, add <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(save the rest for garnish!), <strong>chopped parsley & chives</strong> and<strong> crumbled feta </strong>to the risotto</p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>herby feta risotto</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of water if the risotto is looking a little dry!</p>",
