    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drizzle the <strong>olive tapenade </strong>over<strong> </strong>the <strong>herby feta risotto </strong>and top with<strong> </strong>a <strong>roasted whole tomato</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>dressed salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
